            "content_html": "<div class=\"note info\">\n<p>本章记录有关B站图床使用与项目记录</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"也许b站会变味-但永远不会倒闭\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#也许b站会变味-但永远不会倒闭\">#</a> 也许b站会变味-但永远不会倒闭</h2>\n<h2 id=\"开源地址\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#开源地址\">#</a> 开源地址</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/xlzy520/typora-plugin-bilibili\">点击跳转Github项目</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/b%E7%AB%99%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/domljbndjbjgpkhdbmfgmiclggdfojnd?hl=zh-CN\">点击下载网站插件版</a></p>\n<p>解决防盗链</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">meta</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> name</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">referrer</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> content</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">no-referrer</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://article.biliimg.com/bfs/article/764ef3cdcff955374de67dc6b14f63559a209763.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"b站图床测试图\" /></p>\n",
